title: Don't Hustle Me

description:
Today on the show they opened up the phone lines to hear the thoughts of our listeners about DaBaby almost getting hustled by 2 kids selling candy, should he have gave the kid $200 anyway? Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Joe Biden for his comments on Joe Biden voting speech and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
